          <msContents>
            <summary>Text in praise and honour of the planet Saturn (Śanaiścara) to be employed for recitation, in public or private meditation and prayer. Contains a number of different mantras praising various other planets and Hindu deities (such as Viṣṇu, Śiva, or Gaṇeśa), but especially Saturn.</summary>
            <textLang mainLang="san">In Sanskrit</textLang>
